##  Quick Start

### Prerequisites
```bash
Python 3.x
pandas library
```

### Installation
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/as872832/fraud-detection-project.git
cd fraud-detection-project

# Install dependencies
pip install pandas
```

### Running the System

**Method 1: Python Command**
```bash
python src/detection_system.py
```

**Method 2: Batch File (Windows)**
```bash
run_phase4.bat
```

**With SQL Integration:**
```bash
python src/detection_system_with_db.py
```

