##  Usage Examples

### Generate Transaction Data
```bash
python src/data_generator.py
```

### Run Fraud Detection
```bash
python src/detection_system.py
```

### View SQL Queries
```bash
python src/sql_demo.py
```

### Custom Configuration
```python
from config_manager import ConfigurationManager
from detection_system import FraudDetectionSystem

# Load custom config
system = FraudDetectionSystem()
system.load_configuration('strict')
results = system.run_full_detection()
```

